# PROMO APPROVAL #
# yg bikin promo draft role admin distributor ( principal masih ga bisa )
# approval adalah supervisor diatasnya
# 1. multiple submit draft & rejected yg udah di edit ( perlu flagging ketika rejected sudah di edit )
# 2. edit reject, ada action save and submit, reason nya di replace ga perlu history
# 3. status expired di takeout

